data.description: *ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 2.25%* Amazing opportunity for buyers!  It allows the buyer to purchase a home by taking over the seller's mortgage loan at 2.25% up to $380,000.  Newer construction, rarely available in downtown Lombard! This charming rowhome features gleaming hardwood floors throughout the first level. Custom kitchen opens to family room with fireplace! Oversized granite island with upgraded backsplash, stainless steel appliances and range hood. Enjoy your morning coffee on your spacious front porch. Beautiful craftsman inspired doors and trim. Master bedroom with huge walk-in closet and en suite. Laundry room conventionally located on second floor. Finished lower level. 2 car garage! Prefect downtown location close to Lilacia Park, restaurants,  shopping and expressways! ONE block from Metra Train Station. Living in downtown Lombard is like a dream come true!
